'''Extinguisher foam''' was a fire-fighting measure installed aboard many ships. It could be activated and deactivated from the ship's central control interface and was generally monitored by the ship's computer. Extinguisher foam was also an option for [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droids]].

{{Tech-stub}}

==Other uses==
[[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] used extinguisher foam aboard a crashing [[Drone barge/Legends|drone barge]] to cushion the impact, protecting himself, [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], and [[Tanith Shire]].

In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]], a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]], consisting of Skywalker, [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]], [[Paxin]], [[Falud]], R2-D2 and C-3PO used extinguisher foam to subdue a number of [[Shadow stormtrooper/Legends|Blackhole troopers]] aboard a [[Hrakian]] ship.

